Interface IModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DeterminedNamed, IController, IControlleroid
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplicationManager, DatabaseManager, DialogManager, NetManager

    public interface IModule
extends DeterminedNamed, IController
    A module is a controller that has a determined name and has a determined command header and can access a main controller.
